The student gets a division as per the following rules:

Percentage above or equal to 60 - First division 
Percentage between 50 and 59 - Second division 
Percentage between 40 and 49 - Third division 
Percentage less than 40 - Fail 
Write a program to calculate the division obtained by the student

hindi = float(input('ENTER MARKS : '))
english = float(input('ENTER MARKS : '))
math = float(input('ENTER MARKS : '))
science = float(input('ENTER MARKS : '))
history = float(input('ENTER MARKS : '))

total = (hindi+english+math+science+history)

per = total/5

if hindi <= 40 or english <= 40 or math <= 40 or science <= 40 or history <= 40:
	print('FAIL')
else:
	if per >= 60:
		print('FIRST DIVISION')
	elif per >= 50 and per <= 59:
		print('SECOND DIVISION')
	elif per >= 40 and per <= 49:
		print('THIRD DIVISION')
	else:
		print('FAIL')
